        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you want to store and play the newest Xbox Series X / S games, a normal hard drive won’t do.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: Western Digital&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

